{"tid":2093290,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國外長：歐盟外長下次會議將討論香港問題","createTime":"2020-07-03T17:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T17:35:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"db064172fda2f6925bd6e11f4cc9720d7486871b","tid":2093290,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535705-20200704.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535705-20200704.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IH4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=76639437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535705-20200704.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=616756d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535705-20200704.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n德國外長馬斯表示，歐盟外長將在下次會議，討論香港問題。多個西方國家都對「港區國安法」生效感到憂慮，認為威脅到香港的自由。<br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾早前表示，一國兩制的原則在香港已經遭到侵蝕，歐洲與中國的對話，必須玥立場一致。德國由本月開始，擔任歐盟輪任主席國，預料將向中國提出人權等問題。"},{"pid":"a19c41fd5d4b0883137bd3c38a2a76e8124dda27","tid":2093290,"uid":356218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:35:27.000Z","msg":"依條臭閪就算鳩數啦屌 一手搞死成個歐盟"}]}